  "texts": [
    "The information provided by MBFC assumes a narrow, US-centric world-view.",
    "This is especially prominent when discussing foreign publishers from nations with geopolitical ambitions at odds with the U.S. As such, the metadata provides limited nuance, providing only a single perspective of an inherently subjective assessment.",
    "It is expected that across cultural backgrounds, the publisher information is bound to change.",
    "In general, the news included in the dataset is US-centric, with the vast majority of publishers being American, producing articles for an American audience.",
    "This is exacerbated by us excluding all non-English articles."
  ],
